	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;It is an autonomous organization under the Ministry of Culture, Government of India, dedicated to the promotion of literature in Indian languages.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;Language Eligibility&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;
