		&lt;li&gt;Apart from the 22 languages in the Constitution, the Akademi also recognizes &lt;strong&gt;English&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;Rajasthani&lt;/strong&gt; for its annual awards.&lt;/li&gt;
